SAGE ADK - Agent Development Kit

This project provides a comprehensive Go framework for building secure,
interoperable AI agents with support for A2A and SAGE protocols.

Third-Party Components and Their Licenses:

1. sage (LGPL-3.0-or-later)
   https://github.com/sage-x-project/sage
   Secure Agent Guarantee Engine

2. sage-a2a-go (Apache-2.0)
   https://github.com/sage-x-project/sage-a2a-go
   A2A Protocol Implementation

3. go-ethereum (LGPL-3.0 / GPL-3.0)
   https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum
   Ethereum client and libraries

4. Prometheus Client (Apache-2.0)
   https://github.com/prometheus/client_golang
   Metrics collection and exposition

5. go-openai (Apache-2.0)
   https://github.com/sashabaranov/go-openai
   OpenAI API client

6. go-redis (BSD-2-Clause)
   https://github.com/redis/go-redis
   Redis client for Go

7. lib/pq (MIT)
   https://github.com/lib/pq
   PostgreSQL driver

8. uuid (BSD-3-Clause)
   https://github.com/google/uuid
   UUID generation

For a complete list of dependencies and their licenses, please refer to:
- go.mod file in this repository
- Individual dependency repositories

